{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"id","preciseIdentifier":"c:*Qo","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"metadata":{"title":"init","symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK"}],"externalID":"c:@M@ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK@objc(cs)SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration(im)init","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"}]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/init"},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/init"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}],"title":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration","abstract":[{"text":"The energy management configuration object for a ‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and its subclasses.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and subclasses sport a customizable energy management system.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Since scanners running on a live video feed can put a lot of load onto the CPU and\/or GPU","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of the device, causing the battery to drain quickly and running the device hot, you can customize the energy","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"consumption using this class by configuring the rate of detections\/recognitions per second in performance mode as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"well as in energy saving mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In performance mode the scanners will be fed with a higher, configurable rate of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"video frames per second.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"After a certain, configurable period of inactivity the energy save mode will be engaged and the rate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of scans will be reduced to a lower (configurable) rate.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"You can also configure the time of inactivity before the automatic mode switches from performance to energy save mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Inactivity here means that both of the following conditions are met:","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration/init":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/init","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"init"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"init"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/init","abstract":[],"type":"topic","title":"init"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK":{"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk","type":"topic","title":"ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Version: 8.0.3"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK"}},"variantOverrides":[{"patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK~1SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/title","value":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"},{"op":"replace","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK~1SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/fragments","value":[{"text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}]},{"op":"replace","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK~1SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/navigatorTitle","value":[{"text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}]}],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}]}